bgm.name: オーケストラ・奇妙な感じ・やや暗い・展開がある

parameters: A cry of agony can be heard from nearby...

\n<Man>"A person!? Ah, thank goodness, it's terrible! My child has
been attacked by a monster!"

\n<Woman>"We don't have any healing medicine!? We came empty-handed!
We have nothing!"

\n<Ameria>"A child is injured!? It's okay! I'm a healer! Let me take a
look!"
\n<Ameria>"Eh--ahh! So the one who's injured is...!"

\n<Man>"When the village was attacked, we were chased by monsters.
And in the end, we got lost in this forest! We've been
struggling to survive, but just a moment ago, we were
found..."

\n<Woman>"Ameria-chan! Where's Luerre-san? Isn't Luerre-san here? She
could save this child!"

\n<Ameria>"...The priestess isn't here. I will treat this child's
injuries...!"

\n<Man>"No way! Ameria-chan, you couldn't heal them last time,
could you?"
\n<Ameria>"No--... It's okay. Now, I can definitely do it...!"
\n<Ameria>"Make way! I will surely heal them!"

\n<Man>"Look...! You can't heal them after all! Hurry and find
Luerre-san! To Luerre-san's place...!"
\n<Child>"--Huh. It doesn't hurt... It doesn't hurt anymore!"
\n<Man>"...Really? Are you truly not in pain anymore?"
\n<Child>"Yeah! It's like a lie! My injury healed up in no time!"

\n<Man>"...Ameria-chan, thank you. Truly thank you. I'm sorry for
saying you couldn't heal them."

\n<Ameria>"...No, it's okay. I really couldn't heal them at that
time..."

\n<Woman>"That's not true. Luerre-san told me. It's thanks to Ameria-
chan's hard work that we were saved."

\n<Woman>"We have been saved by you twice now. Ameria-chan is like a
goddess to us. Really, we can't thank you enough. Thank you.
Truly, thank you...!"

\n<Child>"Big sister, thank you! I've decided. I want to become a
healer just like big sister!"

Roselitte and her party turned back once and evacuated the
family to Annabern.
\n<Woman>"Aahh, what should I do! What should I do!"
